        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "CM&DF Dance Honours Performance - Chilliwack Cultural Centre"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Dance Honours Performance is the best of the best in Dance. Features Provincial Delegates as soloists and other award winners as soloists, duos, trio, groups in all genres of Dance; Ballet, Modern, Jazz, Stage, etc. Please come and support all these hard working young dancers, from 6 to 20 as they strive for perfection in their chosen craft."
      }
    ],
